text: Taste Buds is a 2008-10 Canadian and American children's Educational television series. It was Co-Produced by Canadian Studios Nelvana and Marblemedia (Onartio) and American Animation Network Qubo (Florida). It was produced in Association with TVOKids (Onartio) SCN (Saskatchewan) Knowledge Kids (British Columbia) and Access (Alberta). Category:Canadian children's television series
title: Taste Buds (TV series)
